\par 
\par Herewith Report on Berlin Morale No. 36 for the first half of January.
\par 
\par Readers are asked to remember that although this report is compile
d as objectively as possible, opinions expressed may often seem critical and captious. This is because so-called "opinion formers" among the German population may often be ill informed. PORO is not responsible for the views of the German population but is
 concerned only with the accuracy of the reporting.
\par 
